 Nicki Minaj 讲述了过去对 Percocet 的成瘾https://www.nme.com/news/music/nicki-minaj-opens-up-about-past-percocet-addiction-3535695?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=nicki-minaj-opens-up-about-past- Percocet成瘾Surej SinghFri, 10 Nov 2023 05:59:22 +0000 Music NewsNewsRap https://www.nme.com/?p=3535695 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/nicki-minaj@2000x1270.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="" decoding="async" fetchpriority="high" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/nicki-minaj@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/nicki-minaj@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/nicki-minaj@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/nicki-minaj@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/nicki-minaj@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/nicki-minaj@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> “我觉得如果你曾经对任何事情上瘾，你总是必须三思而后行才能做出选择”</p><p> <a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/nicki-minaj-opens-up-about-past-percocet-addiction-3535695">Nicki Minaj 公开谈论过去对 Percocet 成瘾的</a>帖子首先出现在<a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/nicki-minaj@2000x1270.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="" decoding="async" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/nicki-minaj@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/nicki-minaj@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/nicki-minaj@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/nicki-minaj@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/nicki-minaj@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/nicki-minaj@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/nicki-minaj">妮琪·米娜 (Nicki Minaj)</a>讲述了她生命中的一段黑暗时光，当时她曾对 Percocet 上瘾。</p><ul class="post-content-read-more"><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/features/nicki-minaj-every-album-ranked-and-rated-3047363">Nicki Minaj：每张专辑的排名和评级</a></strong></li></ul><p>这位说唱歌手在接受<a href="https://www.vogue.com/article/nicki-minaj-december-cover-2023-interview?utm_term=vogue&amp;utm_social-type=owned&amp;utm_campaign=aud_dev&amp;utm_brand=vogue&amp;utm_source=twitter&amp;utm_medium=social" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>《Vogue》</em></a>杂志封面采访时回忆起自己对处方药上瘾的经历。虽然这位说唱歌手没有透露她何时对 Percocet 上瘾，但她透露，她最初服用这种药物是为了缓解经期痉挛和疼痛。</p><p>然而，她发现自己在不感到疼痛的情况下也在服用Percocet，并且很快意识到自己对它上瘾了。 “没有人告诉我这是一种麻醉剂并且会让人上瘾。幸运的是，我能够让自己接地气。但是——一旦上瘾，就永远上瘾。我觉得如果你曾经对任何东西上瘾，就像我一样，你总是必须三思而后行，做出选择，”米娜告诉<em>《Vogue》</em> 。</p><p>米娜随后解释说，她认为当你经常被监视时，你对药物上瘾的可能性就会更高——这是名气的一个缺点。她提到了其他面临毒瘾问题的著名音乐家，如<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/michael-jackson">迈克尔·杰克逊</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/whitney-houston">惠特尼·休斯顿</a>。 </p><figure id="attachment_3511799" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3511799" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3511799" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Nicki-Minaj-Gilbert-Flores_Variety-via-Getty-Images.jpg" alt="妮琪·米娜" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Nicki-Minaj-Gilbert-Flores_Variety-via-Getty-Images.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Nicki-Minaj-Gilbert-Flores_Variety-via-Getty-Images-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Nicki-Minaj-Gilbert-Flores_Variety-via-Getty-Images-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Nicki-Minaj-Gilbert-Flores_Variety-via-Getty-Images-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Nicki-Minaj-Gilbert-Flores_Variety-via-Getty-Images-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Nicki-Minaj-Gilbert-Flores_Variety-via-Getty-Images-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3511799" class="wp-caption-text">妮琪·米娜。图片来源：Gilbert Flores/Variety via Getty Images</figcaption></figure><p>妮琪·米娜 (Nicki Minaj) 继续说道：“看看我们一些最知名的名人。他们最终要么因为想再出去而被嘲笑，像迈克尔·杰克逊，要么被批评，像惠特尼·休斯顿，要么他们进行无声的战斗，像<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/prince">普林斯</a>。这些都是有史以来最伟大的一些。有一天他们决定，‘你知道吗？我宁愿自我治疗并活在自己的世界里。 ”</p><p>在采访的其他地方，米娜谈到了她父亲以前对可卡因的成瘾，她说她不明白他的药物滥用不是一个选择：“我想看着我的父亲来回走动，我只是希望当时我明白他这样做并不是因为他想这么做。”</p><p> “我认为他是有意识地对毒品上瘾，这种毒品会让他偷走孩子们的电子游戏并卖掉以换取金钱。想想看——谁会有意识地努力做到这一点？现在我意识到，那些人做出这些选择并不是因为他们想伤害他们的家人。毒瘾占据了他们的身体和生活。他们也是受害者。”</p><p> Nicki Minaj 将于 12 月 8 日发行她的下一张专辑“Pink Friday 2”，恰逢她的生日。该唱片最初定于 11 月 17 日发行，但<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/nicki-minaj-delays-new-album-until-her-birthday-3521605">为了避免与她的朋友兼导师 Lil Wayne 与 2 Chainz 的新专辑发生冲突而被推迟</a>。</p><h2><strong>如需有关英国成瘾的帮助、建议或更多信息，请访问<a href="https://talktofrank.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">FRANK 网站</a>。在美国，请访问<a href="https://www.samhsa.gov/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">SAMHSA</a> 。</strong></h2><p> <a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/nicki-minaj-opens-up-about-past-percocet-addiction-3535695">Nicki Minaj 公开谈论过去对 Percocet 成瘾的</a>帖子首先出现在<a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
